{"tid":1838760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［罷工前奏］［拋磚引玉］醫護按章工作","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T09:05:25.000Z","uid":91558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"34962439f6fec10c66eab4164c22c435250f0708","tid":1838760,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"醫護手足<br />\n可能有唔少人會有包袱<br />\n又未試過罷工<br />\n本住救急扶危既心態去做好呢份工<br />\n<br />\n但係去到呢個地步<br />\n政府已經唔理香港人死活<br />\n到時不論黃藍<br />\n全香港都會攬住一齊死<br />\n要解決問題就要搵出病因<br />\n<br />\n希望醫護界既朋友喺新年假期發起按章工作<br />\n以此警告港共 <br />\n唔封關同加強防疫措施就立即進入大罷工<br />\n到時我相信全香港既手足都會支援你地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申學生仔一個<br />\n唔太熟醫護行業<br />\n希望有心人可以幫到醫護手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9c13fa47044af3b3f41fb03df51757e0435dff30","tid":1838760,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c978e9641c6f4ac8fde6768b3a964f2e6e17037","tid":1838760,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:44:53.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"270b4c1f38aab41676a29357ff4e743882854fe0","tid":1838760,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"fff782b933b66b4956bc2df059f6ae0919924bd8","tid":1838760,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d77010fa461d85ac01d5011cfc9a6e802a4c65ca","tid":1838760,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:45:47.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"0461d54e14a086a422d63cfbf67e4d2e6fa0a436","tid":1838760,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"9f0c20daf586e26a26d9b80d647163c710236ff7","tid":1838760,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":